nodes.bodyText:
It looks like this will returns a boolean indicating if it is successful or not, we should probably do something like:
if (!Utils.downMixAudio() || !mVlcPlayer.setAudioDigitalOutputEnabled(true)) {
    mVlcPlayer.setAudioOutput("opensles_android");
}
So it will fallback to downmixing if it fails.

